    "name": "20th Century Swiss Visual Archive",
    "description": {
        "en": "A cross-disciplinary visual archive documenting Swiss cultural life, medical practices, and social transformations throughout the 20th century through photography and film. Combines ethnographic photography from rural and urban Switzerland with scientific medical films from psychiatric institutions.",
